# API Products

# Group Products

## List Products [GET /v1/products{?name__contains,hasTax,code__contains,order}]

Untuk mendapatkan daftar product / item.

+ Parameters
    + name__contains: `Tiket Pesawat` (string, optional) - Searching product by name using method `LIKE`.
    + hasTax: `true` (boolean, optional) - Filtering product by has tax or not.
    + code__contains: `PR-00001` (string, optional) - Searching product by code using method `LIKE`.
    + order: `^code,-coaName` (string, optional) - Sort / order product by code and coaName.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Header

            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2FwaV9pZCI6MywiZXhwIjoxNTUwMDg4NTE0fQ.Jnp0NMZ05zlXs4mKNdbt7cJ4Xwf8mTZrU-PS_eQY-vQ

